2013;;Concussion;;American;;Stacie Passon;;Robin Weigert, Maggie Siff, Ben Shenkman, Janel Moloney;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concussion_(2013_film);;Abby Ableman is a lesbian who becomes disillusioned with her domestic life and career after suffering a mild concussion when her son, Jake, accidentally hits her in the head with a thrown baseball. She then begins working as a prostitute for other women.[4]